name: LOH/DDO 1
description:
#ImaginarywallsNFT is  a collaborative project started by @LasbelsOnHumans and @DDO_xyz in which 2 or more artists come together and digitally merge their works, creating a synergy.

Simply,  a host’ image in which one or more ‘guest’ images are placed. 

All proceeds from the project are split equally between contributing parties. 

It’s hoped that using #imaginarywallsNFT when posting becomes a clear indication of an artists willingness to work on similar collaborations of their own. 

As ‘we’re all early’ this can be seen as a useful way of sharing and  cross pollinating one another’s audience with the potential to grow both and have creative fun and develop our practice whilst doing so.
